  "title": "Investment Analyst (Private Banking)",
  "description": "<p>about the company</p><p>Our client is a leading global private bank.</p><p>about the job</p><ul><li><p>Support the evaluation of performance and risk metrics for diverse multi-asset portfolios.</p></li><li><p>Assist the Quantitative team in building and refining tools designed for the management of multi-asset strategies.</p></li><li><p>Conduct both quantitative and qualitative assessments of investment vehicles, while supporting the coordination of related operational and trading requirements.</p></li><li><p>Contribute to the formulation of tactical investment views and implementation strategies across asset classes, including equities, fixed income, currencies, and commodities.</p></li><li><p>Assist in managing global multi-asset portfolios for discretionary private and institutional clients.</p></li></ul><p>To apply online please use the 'apply' function.</p><p><strong>(EA: 94C3609/ R24124496)</strong></p>",
